{"tid":2398298,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"飛鵝山現「蝈安吃孩」直幡","createTime":"2021-02-07T07:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T07:26:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d49bf3b85b381ec6c971c1a22c00a1aca993be5a","tid":2398298,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210207/GQ2J7XHFOJCJBFELYNCEMIJ4BU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210207%2FGQ2J7XHFOJCJBFELYNCEMIJ4BU%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOXJTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=97fb4fa8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210207%2FGQ2J7XHFOJCJBFELYNCEMIJ4BU%2F&h=6aa274dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210207/GQ2J7XHFOJCJBFELYNCEMIJ4BU/</a><br />\n<br />\n飛鵝山現「蝈安吃孩」直幡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Q77W9u1LDoFyd8FhrEuls3OzxuQ=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MWA3VRY5MJAOPCXNM33RVQWB7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQ77W9u1LDoFyd8FhrEuls3OzxuQ%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMWA3VRY5MJAOPCXNM33RVQWB7A.jpg&h=70ec6100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■飛鵝山腰昨現「蝈安狗吃孩子的血！」直幡，其後被拆走。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國安法實施後，街頭及山頭抗爭同遭封殺，獅子山、九龍筆架山及油塘魔鬼山三個掛直幡熱門地，岩壁上的金屬掛片去年遭消防及警方清除。惟政府禁言，人心不死，直幡昨於飛鵝山再現，為黑底白字寫上「蝈安狗吃孩子的血！」的字句，消防其後到場移除。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消防到場移除<br />\n<br />\n昨早約7時許，飛鵝山山腰位置，有市民懸掛一幅直幡，黑底白字寫上「蝈安狗吃孩子的血！」。直幡高掛在山腰岩壁之上，新舊清水灣道和部份東九龍地方，均可清楚看到。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n去年七一前，即國安法實施前夕，警方率先拆除獅子山東面岩壁一個掛片，隨着多個抗爭周年活動逼近，魔鬼山山坡的掛片亦遭「鋼膠」封死，直至八月，有市民發現警方高姿態派出衝鋒車上山拆掛片。政府拆掛片造法引來攀山者批評，指若掛片被劏開，切口有機會割傷他人，或割斷安全繩，令攀山者跌落懸崖。"}]}